[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Key Technical Findings:                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **1. YAML Deserialization (FILTERED)**                                       [32m│[0m
