[32m│[0m - **Vector**: PyYAML unsafe loading (`yaml.load()`)                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Status**: Malicious `!!python/object/apply` payloads are **detected and  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m reset** to `W10K` (empty list)                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Exploitable**: NO - validation is in place                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
